<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>选择：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The Internet increased options of movie lovers.
互联网增加了电影爱好者的选择。</p><footer>2017 江苏书面表达</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You <strong>have no option but to</strong> (= have to) refuse his proposal.
